HEADWORD: Tempting
<hw>Tempt"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Adapted to entice or allure;
attractive; alluring; seductive; enticing; <as>as, <ex>tempting</ex>
pleasures</as>.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Tempt"ing*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos> -- <wf>Tempt"ing*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

